In this article are listed various tutorials, in various forms, to help you understand and better know the details of _Sugimori style_.

For any fan game creator of the Pokémon universe, the name of **Ken Sugimori** is known and respected. Designer of the original artworks for the Pokémon games, he also made artworks for the movies and the trading card game.

For the older ones among us, or simply the most collectors, he is the designer of many cards of the first series released in the late 90s.

{% cta href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ken_Sugimori" align="left" %}Read more about Ken Sugimori{% /cta %}

## How to draw Pokémon {% id="how-to-draw-pokemon" %}

To learn how to draw Pokémon (and thus your own Fakemon), here is a list of some tutorials:

- [Ken Sugimori Tutorial](https://www.deviantart.com/nachtbeirmann/art/Ken-Sugimori-Tutorial-Pt-1-420735324 "Ken Sugimori Tutorial"), by [NachtBeirmann](https://www.deviantart.com/nachtbeirmann "NachtBeirmann")
- [Make a Sugimori artwork](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cpnw4CdC0sA "Make a Sugimori artwork"), a speedpaint Youtube video by [PinkGermy](https://www.deviantart.com/pinkgermy "PinkGermy")
- [3 videos tutorial](https://www.deviantart.com/devildman/art/How-to-Draw-Sugimori-Style-Pokemon-Tutorial-619567075 "3 videos tutorial") (links in description), by [DevilDman](https://www.deviantart.com/devildman "DevilDman")
- [How to draw Pokémon like Ken Sugimori](https://www.deviantart.com/generalgibby/art/Photoshop-How-to-Draw-Pokemon-Like-Ken-Sugimori-400890062 "How to draw Pokémon line Ken Sugimori") (on Photoshop), by [GeneralGibby](https://www.deviantart.com/generalgibby "GeneralGibby")

## How to draw characters {% id="how-to-draw-characters" %}

To learn how to draw characters in the style of Pokémon, here is a list of some tutorials:

- [How I draw in Pokémon style](https://www.deviantart.com/shootingstar03/art/How-I-draw-in-Pokemon-style-350280800 "How I draw in Pokémon style"), by [ShootingStar03](https://www.deviantart.com/shootingstar03 "ShootingStar03")
- [Tutorial: Character Design](https://www.deviantart.com/ky-nim/art/Tutorial-Character-Design-317797007 "Tutorial about Character Design"), by [ky-nim](https://www.deviantart.com/ky-nim "ky-nim")

## To go further

Feel free to take as many references as possible when drawing, to train your eyes and improve your reflexes on the style of Pokémon artists like [Take](https://twitter.com/takegarou), [Megumi Mizutani](https://twitter.com/megtany), [Ken Sugimori](https://twitter.com/SUPER_32X) or [Yusuke Omura](https://twitter.com/yusuke_omura).

